Reasoning: The paper discusses a software platform for building performance design and management, which involves modeling, data analysis, and visualization. This falls under the scope of software engineering (cs.SE), computer engineering (cs.CE), and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of state graphs and a domain-specific language also suggests the application of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and programming languages (cs.PL) in the development of the Energy Navigator.
